@startuml
title Attraction Publication - 3.6 (AttractionPublicationStatus)
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam state {
  BackgroundColor #EEECFB
  BorderColor #8B7FD6
  FontColor #1A1A1A
  ArrowColor #444444
}
hide empty description

[*] --> PAUSED : Attraction created (default)
PAUSED --> ACTIVE : First approval /\nPartner opens selling
ACTIVE --> PAUSED : Partner pauses selling
ACTIVE --> ARCHIVED : Partner archives
PAUSED --> ARCHIVED : Partner archives
ARCHIVED --> [*]

ACTIVE : On public listings\n(if status = APPROVED)
PAUSED : Hidden from sale
@enduml
